<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 22:07:24 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>加拿大对西岸著名的以色列定居者领导人和组织实施制裁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/canada-imposes-sanctions-on-prominent-israeli-settler-leaders-organizations-in-west-bank/00000190-5ac4-d63a-a7b2-5fdf96230000</link><description>加拿大是第一个制裁约旦河西岸主要定居点组织阿马纳的政府，该组织表示其目标是在约旦河西岸安置 100 万定居者</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 18:16:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/canada-imposes-sanctions-on-prominent-israeli-settler-leaders-organizations-in-west-bank/00000190-5ac4-d63a-a7b2-5fdf96230000</guid></item><item><title>拜登与特朗普的辩论将是美国对以色列战争的前所未有的展示</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-27/ty-article/.highlight/biden-trump-debate-will-be-an-unprecedented-display-of-americas-wars-over-israel/00000190-590a-def3-a5b6-db2f35450000</link><description>以色列或反犹太主义很少成为美国总统辩论的核心问题。这一次，他们很可能扮演主角，尽管有些不和谐</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 17:26:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-27/ty-article/.highlight/biden-trump-debate-will-be-an-unprecedented-display-of-americas-wars-over-israel/00000190-590a-def3-a5b6-db2f35450000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 265 天：监管机构警告称，以色列不准备在发生战争时从北部撤离</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-265-israel-not-ready-to-evacuate-north-in-case-of-war-watchdog-warns/00000190-5a95-def3-a5b6-dab7b76b0001</link><description>美国官员警告以色列，即使在黎巴嫩南部进行有限的地面行动也可能导致与伊朗的地区战争 ■ 居民告诉《国土报》，以色列国防军猛烈轰炸加沙城 Zeitoun 社区 Shujaiyeh ■ 美国、德国和荷兰警告其公民不要前往黎巴嫩 ■ 三据报道，以色列在大马士革以南发动的袭击中丧生 ■ 战争进入 265 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 16:50:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-265-israel-not-ready-to-evacuate-north-in-case-of-war-watchdog-warns/00000190-5a95-def3-a5b6-dab7b76b0001</guid></item><item><title>人质和10月7日受害者家属请愿以色列最高法院成立调查委员会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/hostages-and-oct-7-victims-families-petition-high-court-establish-commission-of-inquiry/00000190-59f9-d63a-a7b2-5dff68f90000</link><description>“负责以色列公众福祉的人们必须为自己在这场灾难中所扮演的角色承担责任”：请愿者要求调查委员会调查导致 10 月 7 日哈马斯致命袭击的原因</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 16:36:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/hostages-and-oct-7-victims-families-petition-high-court-establish-commission-of-inquiry/00000190-59f9-d63a-a7b2-5dff68f90000</guid></item><item><title>美国警告以色列：即使是有限的南黎巴嫩演习也可能导致真主党与伊朗战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/u-s-warns-israel-even-limited-south-lebanon-maneuver-could-lead-to-hezbollah-iran-war/00000190-59d2-d506-ab9a-79fa5e310000</link><description>一名美国官员在最近与以色列国防官员会面时表示，即使以色列发誓只想将真主党赶出边境，并不想摧毁贝鲁特，对方也可能不会相信。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 15:57:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/u-s-warns-israel-even-limited-south-lebanon-maneuver-could-lead-to-hezbollah-iran-war/00000190-59d2-d506-ab9a-79fa5e310000</guid></item><item><title>令人眼花缭乱的速度，然后下降：美国对以色列的武器运输如何放缓</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/a-dizzying-pace-then-a-drop-how-u-s-arms-shipments-to-israel-slowed-down/00000190-59b6-dc65-abff-79bff9b10000</link><description>公开的航班跟踪数据显示，自加沙战争爆发以来，每个月有多少美国武器抵达以色列，交付速度急剧上升，然后逐渐放缓</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 15:17:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/a-dizzying-pace-then-a-drop-how-u-s-arms-shipments-to-israel-slowed-down/00000190-59b6-dc65-abff-79bff9b10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列法院命令本-格维尔部披露有关非法发放枪支许可证的信息</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/court-orders-ben-gvirs-ministry-to-disclose-info-about-unlawful-issuance-of-gun-licenses/00000190-59f9-def3-a5b6-dbffac870000</link><description>以色列法院命令极右翼议员伊塔马尔·本·格维尔领导的国家安全部向调查人员提供与他的雇员非法分发枪支许可证有关的文件。警方消息人士称，调查被推迟是因为担心这会导致对本-格维尔本人的怀疑</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 15:16:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/court-orders-ben-gvirs-ministry-to-disclose-info-about-unlawful-issuance-of-gun-licenses/00000190-59f9-def3-a5b6-dbffac870000</guid></item><item><title>“没有出路”：以色列 80 年代流行歌星亚当去世</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-80s-pop-star-adam-dies/00000190-59d8-de5e-abd0-fbfac8f70000</link><description>Adam 是 80 年代和 90 年代初最伟大的以色列流行偶像之一。他在遗言中说道：“我感谢这一生的美好旅程。”他要求在去世后发表遗言。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 14:45:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-80s-pop-star-adam-dies/00000190-59d8-de5e-abd0-fbfac8f70000</guid></item><item><title>“回家”：耶路撒冷博物馆鼓动犹太人“征服并定居”整个加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/visiting-the-jerusalem-museum-that-agitates-for-jews-to-conquer-and-settle-all-of-gaza/00000190-58a9-ddd9-a1f1-dafbe4b80000</link><description>古什卡蒂夫博物馆是一个由极右翼拉比和前定居者建立的“非政治性”私人企业，它的时间远没有被冻结：战争期间，其收藏的烛台被以色列国防军士兵“征用”在加沙点燃，而博物馆导游侮辱阿拉伯人，并对加沙和黎巴嫩南部的新定居点感到兴奋</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 14:44:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/visiting-the-jerusalem-museum-that-agitates-for-jews-to-conquer-and-settle-all-of-gaza/00000190-58a9-ddd9-a1f1-dafbe4b80000</guid></item><item><title>萨拉·内塔尼亚胡呼吁美国第一夫人要求无条件释放以色列国防军女观察员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/sara-netanyahu-calls-on-first-lady-to-demand-unconditional-release-of-idf-female-spotters/00000190-59a9-ddd9-a1f1-dbfb50fd0000</link><description>在给吉尔·拜登的第二封信中，总理夫人要求第一夫人与她和观察者的母亲一起领导一个联盟，推动将女孩从哈马斯的囚禁中解救出来。此举是内塔尼亚胡与人质家属之间有些坎坷的关系的一部分</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 14:03:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/sara-netanyahu-calls-on-first-lady-to-demand-unconditional-release-of-idf-female-spotters/00000190-59a9-ddd9-a1f1-dbfb50fd0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列悲伤专家：“我们不区分加沙儿童和哈马斯努赫巴部队”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/we-dont-distinguish-between-a-child-in-gaza-and-hamas-nukhba-force/00000190-4a6f-da60-a5b7-cfef76da0000</link><description>自战争开始以来，心理健康专家兼作家梅拉夫·罗斯（Yair Lapid 的妹妹兼红颜知己）一直在治疗人们的创伤。现在她担心这场灾难对社会造成的后果：“报复每个人的愿望对我们来说非常危险”</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 13:33:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/we-dont-distinguish-between-a-child-in-gaza-and-hamas-nukhba-force/00000190-4a6f-da60-a5b7-cfef76da0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队暂停在反政府抗议活动中被拘留的士兵的预备役义务</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-suspends-reserve-duty-for-soldiers-detained-at-anti-government-protests/00000190-590c-ddd9-a1f1-dbfe96960000</link><description>据军方称，在收到警方报告后，预备役军人的服役将暂时停止，直至案件审理结束，并且预备役军人可以对决定提出上诉。 “我不敢相信这会自动发生，”一名被停职的预备役军人阿隆·格鲁佐夫 (Alon Gruzov) 说道，他在一次抗议活动中挡住了臭鼬水炮。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 13:27:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-suspends-reserve-duty-for-soldiers-detained-at-anti-government-protests/00000190-590c-ddd9-a1f1-dbfe96960000</guid></item><item><title>荷兰外交部召见以色列大使澄清涉嫌对国际刑事法院检察官进行间谍活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/netherlands-summons-israeli-ambassador-to-clarify-alleged-spying-of-icc-prosecutors/00000190-5971-d63a-a7b2-5d7f66690000</link><description>在对以色列近十年来对国际刑事法院及其官员进行秘密监视的调查公布后，该部发言人表示，几名荷兰议员对这些指控表示了担忧</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 13:21:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/netherlands-summons-israeli-ambassador-to-clarify-alleged-spying-of-icc-prosecutors/00000190-5971-d63a-a7b2-5d7f66690000</guid></item><item><title>正统派“正常化”可能会解决征兵问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/haredi-normalization-may-solve-the-conscription-problem/00000190-599e-d7e5-a1f3-dd9f80b10000</link><description>经济压力迫使极端正统派变得更像其他以色列人。还有什么比在军队服役更以色列化的呢？</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 12:23:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/haredi-normalization-may-solve-the-conscription-problem/00000190-599e-d7e5-a1f3-dd9f80b10000</guid></item><item><title>今年已有 103 名阿拉伯人在以色列被杀，案件破案率急剧下降</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/103-arabs-have-been-killed-in-israel-this-year-as-rate-of-solved-cases-steeply-declines/00000190-582a-ddd9-a1f1-dafad2e60000</link><description>以色列警方一名高级官员表示，面对阿拉伯社会暴力犯罪的增加，以色列警方“无能为力”，自本-格维尔担任国家安全部长以来的 18 个多月里，凶杀案增加了一倍多</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 12:05:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/103-arabs-have-been-killed-in-israel-this-year-as-rate-of-solved-cases-steeply-declines/00000190-582a-ddd9-a1f1-dafad2e60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军官在约旦河西岸杰宁袭击中发生爆炸，造成16人受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-officer-killed-16-wounded-by-explosion-ambush-in-raid-on-west-banks-jenin/00000190-5915-d506-ab9a-797fc36b0000</link><description>爆炸造成 16 人受伤，爆炸发生时以色列国防军和以色列安全部队正在约旦河西岸的杰宁执行任务。以色列国防军表示，军用推土机在部队进入之前扫描了该地区</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 11:45:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-officer-killed-16-wounded-by-explosion-ambush-in-raid-on-west-banks-jenin/00000190-5915-d506-ab9a-797fc36b0000</guid></item><item><title>1948年，犹太学院只有400名学生：多年来以色列的军事豁免</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/only-400-yeshiva-students-in-1948-israels-military-exemptions-through-the-years/00000190-592c-def3-a5b6-db2fe28b0000</link><description>本·古里安在 1948 年给予犹太学院的学生豁免权，但十年后问道：“一位母亲的儿子为了保卫祖国而被杀，而另一位母亲的儿子则安全地坐在自己的房间里学习，这是否合适？” &amp;#39;</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 11:09:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/only-400-yeshiva-students-in-1948-israels-military-exemptions-through-the-years/00000190-592c-def3-a5b6-db2fe28b0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争限制了以色列电影的成功，但本土电影继续在海外获奖</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/film/2024-06-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/gaza-war-limits-israeli-cinemas-success-but-local-films-continue-to-win-awards-overseas/00000190-5875-def3-a5b6-da77936b0000</link><description>两部以色列电影刚刚在著名的国际电影节上放映，其中一部——汤姆·内舍尔的《走近》——甚至在纽约翠贝卡电影节上获奖。但这些仅仅是证明规则的例外吗？</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 10:06:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/film/2024-06-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/gaza-war-limits-israeli-cinemas-success-but-local-films-continue-to-win-awards-overseas/00000190-5875-def3-a5b6-da77936b0000</guid></item><item><title>总理办公室指责以色列医院侵犯获救人质的隐私</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/prime-ministers-office-accuses-israeli-hospital-of-violating-rescued-hostages-privacy/00000190-5605-dc65-abff-7e2f14800000</link><description>总理办公室在一次没有医院代表出席的会议上表示，“医院工作人员不断给人质拍照，他们的照片未经同意就被分享，医疗队披露了有关他们被囚禁和健康状况的详细信息”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 09:38:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article/.premium/prime-ministers-office-accuses-israeli-hospital-of-violating-rescued-hostages-privacy/00000190-5605-dc65-abff-7e2f14800000</guid></item><item><title>三名以色列陆军预备役军人解释为什么他们拒绝继续在加沙服役</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/three-israeli-army-reservists-explain-why-they-refuse-to-continue-serving-in-gaza/00000190-5014-d3c0-a5d4-737644c90000</link><description>尤瓦尔被要求烧毁两栋住宅楼；迈克尔意识到在他观察到的每次爆炸中可能有多少平民丧生；当以色列进入拉法时，塔尔崩溃了。他们愿意为拒绝在加沙服役而付出代价</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 07:45:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/three-israeli-army-reservists-explain-why-they-refuse-to-continue-serving-in-gaza/00000190-5014-d3c0-a5d4-737644c90000</guid></item></channel></rss>